# sections.  Make sure the config section is ok.  
# Must 'make install' before proceeding to tests.  
#
# Test writing guidelines:
#     - read Makefile, run_tests, run_test, libemul.tst
#     - use the keywords "success" and "FAILED" in your messages
#     - use the "**** " as a prefix in your messages
#     - use print_red for error messages, print_blue for markers 
#     - all value names must start with $CFGS_TST_PREFIX. 
#       Ex: "$CFGS_TST_PREFIX/network/eth0/ip"
#       (this value space will be destroyed)
#     - return 0 on success, 1 on error
#     - use .tst extension for active tests 
#     - when adding a test to the list below:
#         - keep order - tests' order is important
#         - add it also in the daemon section if appropriate 
